### Lessons API
### Base URL: /api/v1/data/lessons/

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1/data

### Get all published lessons
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/ HTTP/1.1

### Get lesson by UUID
# Replace with actual UUID from the list response
@lessonUuid = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonUuid}}/ HTTP/1.1

### Get non-existent lesson (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/ HTTP/1.1
